start.body:
Haddii lagaa helay cudurka COVID-19 (baaritaan aan ahayn kan ah ka baarka unugyada difaaca jirka), si qarsoodi ah ayaad usoo sheegi kartaa natiijada baaritaanka.

Soo gudbinta baaritaankaagu waxay ka caawin kartaa dadka kale ee deegaankaaga inay iska ilaaliyaan faafidda fayraska.

user_details_form.subheader: Fadlan sheeg taariikhda baaritaankaaga iyo nambarka taleefanka.

export.complete_body_bluetooth: Ayaad markaa gacan ka geysaneysaa xakameynta faafitaanka fayraska iyo inaad badbaadiso dadka kale ee bulshadaada ka tirsan.
export.consent_body_0: Wadaagista ka helitaankaaga toganaha ahi waa ikhtiyaari oo waxa kaliya ee lagu samayn karaa oggolaanshahaaga.
export.consent_body_2: Macluumaadka kaliya ee la wadaagi doono ayaa noqonaya koox tirooyin bakhtiyaanasiibaka ah ee telefankaagu kala kala beddehsay Bluetooth-ka telefoonka kale ee ka ag dhawaa 14kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay, oo ay weheliso dhibco halis la misaamay oo ku saleysan goorta ay astaamahaagu ay soo baxeen.
export.consent_warning_message: Inaad sii wado waxay baabi'inaysaa koodhkaaga baaritaanka lagaaga helay caabuqa. Haddii aad doonayso inaad nala wadaagto xogta baaritaanka caabuqa lagaaga helay mustaqbalka danbe, waxaad marka koobaad u baahan doontaa inaad hesho koodh cusub oo muujinaaya in caabuqa lagaa helay.

verification_code_info.info_body:
Koodhka xaqiijintu waa koodh ay ku siinayaan maamulka caafimaadku, {{healthAuthorityName}}, haddii aad hesho natiijada caabuqa lagaaga helay.

Koodhka xaqiijinta waxaa loo adeegsadaa xaqiijinta in natiijada baarista caabuqa lagaaga helay ay sax tahay.

Koodh kasta oo xaqiijin wuxuu dhacayaa kadib muddo kooban si loo xaqiijiyo inaan la gudbin baaritaano been ah.

Haddii aad waajahdo cilad markaad gudbinayso koodhkaaga xaqiijinta, waxaa qasab ah inaad koodh cusub ka hesho maamulka caafimaadka kahor intaadan gudbin markale.
verification_code_info.what_happens_body:
Markaad gudbiso koodhkaaga xaqiijinta, abka ayaa ku waydiin doona inaad la wadaagto furayaasha sikudhafan ee loo diraayo dadka kula joogay oo ka imaanaaya aaladaha aad ag joogtay.

Haddii aad ogolaansho siiso, abka ayaa furayaashaan u diraaya seerfarka ogaysiiska U dhawaanshaha Qofka caabuqa qaba. Seerfarka ogaysiiska ayaa u sheegaaya aaladaha aad u dhawayd natiijada baaritaanka caabuqa lagaaga helay.

Abku marna ma aruursho ama ma kaydsho xogtaada shaqsiga ah. Kaliya furayaasha iskudhafan ee qarsoodiga ah ee ku jira aaladaada ayaa aaladaha kale lala wadaagayaa.
verification_code_info.what_happens_header: Maxaa dhacaaya marka aan gudbiyo koodhkayga?

onboarding.notification_body1: Waxaad heli doontaa ogeysiinnada markaad meel uun aad ku kulanteen qof ka warbixiyay inuu u noqday togane cudurka COVID-19.
onboarding.notification_body2: Aabka ayaa ku sameeyaa sidaa isaga oo adeegsanaya Bluetooth Low Energy (Tamar HooseBluetooth) oo wuxuu ilaaliyaa koodhadhka bakhtiyaanasiibka iyada oo aanu garanyn qofkaad tahay ama meesha aad tagtay. Waad ka damin kartaa mar kasta gudaha dejimaha.
onboarding.notification_header: Ha lagula socodsiiyo haddii laga yaabaa ay dhacdo inaad ufeydsantay
onboarding.notification_subheader3: Aabkan kaama ilaalin doono caabuqa COVID-19.

protect_privacy.body_1: Koodhadhka kuma jiraan wax macluumaad shaqsiyeed ah waxayna beddelaan 10-20 daqiiqo kasta si loo ilaaliyo aqoonsigaaga.
protect_privacy.body_2: Telefoonnada ayay isweydaarsadaan koodhadhka aaladaha kale istcimaalya Tamar Hoose Bluetooth. Taasi waxay u oggolaanaysaa {{applicationName}} inuu raadraaco kulannadaada maalinlaha ah si aan adigu qof aad la garanayn, xitaa marka aanay ka gurnayn aaladdaada.
protect_privacy.body_3: Kaddib marka la noqdo togane ka ijaabinta COVID-19, isticmaaleyaasha ayaa la wadaagi kare koodh fure ah {{applicationName}} si loo xaqiijiyo ka helkooda cudurka. Hadday taa sameeyaan, koodhadhkooda dhawaanta ahaa ee telefoonnadooda ayaa loo haadin doonaa oo si xasilan kor loogu rari doonaa serferka. Nidaamkan xaqiijintu waxay waxtar u leedahay kahortagga warbixinnada toganaha khaladka ah (false positive report).
protect_privacy.body_4: Haddii aqoonsi la calaamadeeyay ay iswaafaqaan aqoonsi ku keydsan taleefankaaga, tani waxay muujineysaa inaad la kulantay qof laga helay cudurka COVID-19. Tan waa sida {{applicationName}} go'aamin kara haddii adiga ay dhici karto in fayraska aad u feydsantay
protect_privacy.body_5:
Haddii uu jiro iswaafaqsanaan, {{applicationName}} ayaa ku ogeysiin doona oo ku siin doona hagitaan dheeraad ah oo ka socda waaxdaada caafimaadka.

Tani waa sida {{applicationName}} uu awood uu kuu siin karo inaad go'aan ka gaarto waxyaabo ku saabsan caafimaadkaaga, oo aad ammaanka bulshadaada ku ilaaliso, dhammaantood iyadoon la ogeyn cidda aad tahay iyo halka aad joogtay.
protect_privacy.subheader_1: Markaad daarto Raadinta U dhowaanshaha (Proximity Tracing) taleefankaaga waxaa lagu calaamadeeyaa si isdaba-joog ah oo is beddelaya, aqoonsiyo qori-tuur ah
protect_privacy.subheader_2: Telefoonnada raadraacidda u dhawaanshaha kartida loo siisay koodhadh ku kala beddelashada aaladaha kale ee ay la kulmaan
protect_privacy.subheader_3: Markuu adeegsade baaritaanka laga helo, waxay dooran karaan inay si qarsoodi ah ula wadaagaan xaaladdooda caafimaad
protect_privacy.subheader_4: Telefoon kasta wuxuu marba sarfarka ugu baaqaa liiska aqoonsiyada la calaamadeeyay wuxuu raadiyaa mid waafaqa
protect_privacy.subheader_5: Waa lagugu soo wargelin doonaa haddii {{applicationName}} helo qof laga helay oo togane ah aqoonsi la calaamadeeyay

guidance.if_symptoms_develop: Haddii aad isku aragto wax kamid ah astaamaha COVID-19 ama xanuunkaagu kasii daro, wac bixiyahaaga daryeela caafimaadka, laynka talooyinka caafimaadka, ama adeeg bixiyaha caafimaadka taleefanka lagu baxsho.
guidance.may_help_you_feel_better: Halkaan waxaad ka helaysaa talaabooyinka qaar kuwaas oo kaa caawin kara inaad xanuunka ka bogsooto:
guidance.monitor_your_symptoms: Waan ka xunnahay inaad bukto. Guriga joog oo la soco astaamahaaga. Wac adeeg bixiyahaaga haddii astaamaha xanuunkaagu kasii daraan, gurigana joog.
guidance.protect_others: Qaad tallaabooyinkaan si ay kaaga caawiyaan inaad dadka kale ka difaacdo xanuunka.
guidance.seek_medical_care: Haddii aad isleedahay waa xaalad degdeg ah ama xanuunkaagu kasii daro, raadso daryeel caafimaad.
guidance.stay_6_feet_away: Ka fogow ugu yaraan 6 fiit dadka kale kana fogoow goobaha saxmada iyo buuqa badan.
guidance.stay_at_home: Guriga joog marka laga reebo inaad raadsanayso daryeel caafimaad.
guidance.stay_away_from_higher_risk_people: Haddii ay suuragalayso, ka fogow dadka khatarta wayn ugu jira inay aad ugu xanuunsadaan COVID-19.
guidance.take_care_of_yourself: Baro sida loo daryeelo naftaada ama qof kale oo jirran.
guidance.take_temperature: Laba jeer cabbir heer kulkaaga maalintii oo la socoto astaamaha xanuunka COVID-19.
guidance.you_have_underlying_conditions: Waan ka xunnahay inaad xanuunsan tahay. Astaamahaaga ayaa la xariiri kara COVID-19. Waxaad sidoo kale qabtaa xaalado caafimaad oo khatar wayn kuu gelin kara inaad xanuun xun ka qaado caabuqa.
guidance.your_symptoms_might_be_related: Waan ka xunnahay inaad xanuunsan tahay. Astaamahaaga ayaa la xariiri kara COVID-19.

intro.find_out_how_to_care: Raadi qaabka aad u daryeelayso naftaada iyo dadka kale kadib markaad la joogtay qof qaba caabuqa COVID-19.
intro.if_this_is: Haddii xanuunkaagu yahay xaalad degdeg ah, fadlan wac {{emergencyPhoneNumber}}
intro.learn_more: Xog dheeraad ah ka ogoow Aalada Is qiimaynta Iskaa ah ee Korona Fayraska ee CDC ee Qiimayntaan Shaqsiga ah lagu saleeyay
intro.this_is_based_on: Tan waxaa lagu salaynayaa tilmaantii ugu danbaysay ee kasoo baxday CDC oo wayna isbaddali kartaa muddo kadib markaan xog dheeraad ah ka helno sida u  fayrasku u faafoiyo xanuunka ka dhashaba
intro.you_are_a_resident: Waxaad daggan tahay deegaan taageero ka hela {{ healthAuthorityName }}

underlying_conditions.blood_disorder: Xanuunka dhiigga, sida xanuunka unug majada (sickle cell) ama cudrka cassanka oo dhiigga ku yaraada (thalassemia)
underlying_conditions.cerebrovascular_disease: Xanuunka maskaxda ama xanuunka neerfaha garaadka, sida faaligga ama asaasaqa
underlying_conditions.do_you_have: Ma qabtaa wax kamid ah xanuunnada soo socda?
underlying_conditions.heart_condition: Xanuunka wadnaha oo daran, sida hawlgabka wadnaha, xanuunka halbawlaha dhiigga wadnaha, ama xanuunka murqaha wadnaha
underlying_conditions.lung_disease: Xanuunka sanbabbada oo daran, sida neefta heerka dhexe ilaa heerka daran, COPD, xanuunka naqaska (cystic fibrosis), ama xanuunka wadnaha
underlying_conditions.select_all_or_none: Dooro dhammaan meelaha ku quseeya (ama midna)
underlying_conditions.weakened_immune_system: Nidaamka difaaca jirka oo daciifay ama cunista daawooyinka keena in nidaamka difaaca jirku daciifo.

settings.delete_data_disclosure1: Marka aad taabato batoonka "Delete My Data (Tir Xogtayda)" ee hoose, abka ayaa tiri doona xogta ku jirta Taariikhda Astaamaha ee lagu kaydiyay taleefankaaga.
settings.delete_data_disclosure2:
Talaabadaan ma tirayso xogta uu abuuray ama aruurshay taleefankaagu ee qusaysa Ogaysiiska Ufeydsanaanta.

Waxaad xogtaan dheeraadka ah ka tiri karaa adoo galaaya qaybta Settings-ka ee aaladaada.
settings.delete_data_language_token: Boono ku jirta aaladaada oo kaydinaysa dookhaaga luuqada
settings.delete_data_onboarding_token: Boono ku jirta aaladaada oo kaydinaysa markaad dhamayso xog ku shubida abka
settings.delete_data_product_analytics: Boono ku jirta aaladaada oo kaydinaysa markaad ogolaato inaad la wadaagto xogta qiimaynta badeecada
settings.delete_data_symptom_history: Kaydadka xogta astaamaha oo u jira aaladaada
settings.delete_data_this_action: Talaabadaan waxay tiraysaa dhammaan xogta ku jirta {{applicationName}}.

errors.deleting_data: Waan ka xunahay, ma tiri karno xogtaada

errors.updating_symptoms: Waan ka xunnahay, waan cusboonaysiin kari waynay astaamahaaga

sharing.header: Taariikhda Astaamaha xanuunka laga soo bilaabo {{startDate}} ilaa {{endDate}}
sharing.no_symptoms_were_logged: Ma jiraan wax astaamo ah oo la qoray
sharing.you_did_not_feel_well: Si fiican ma aadan dareemayn, astaamaha waxaa ku jiray: {{symptomList}}

symptom_history.to_protect_your_privacy: Si loo difaaco sirtaada, xogta aad geliso ayaa lagu kaydiyaa aaladdaada oo si ootomaatig ah ayaana loo tiraa {{days}} maalmood kadib.

symptom.bluish_lips_or_face: Bishimaha  ama wajiga oo midka buluugga oo kale noqda
symptom.inability_to_wake_or_stay_awake: Aad awoodi waydo inaad toosto ama soo jeeddo
symptom.new_loss_of_taste_or_smell: Luminta dhadhanka ama urka oo cusub
symptom.persistent_pain_or_pressure_in_the_chest: Dhibaato kaa haysata neefsiga ama cadaadis kaa fuula xabadka
symptom.shortness_of_breath_or_difficulty_breath: Neefta oo ku yaraata ama dhibaato dhanka neefsiga ah

verification_code_alerts.code_used_body: Koodhka xaqiijinta ee aad bixisay horay ayaa loo isticmaalay.
verification_code_alerts.code_used_title: Koodhka Xaqiijinta Mar hore ayaa La isticmaalay
verification_code_alerts.invalid_code_body:
Koodhka xaqiijinta ee aad soo gudbisay waa khalad.

Koodhku waa inuu yahay koodhka xaqiijinta oo sax ah oo ay u siiyeen maamulkaaga caafimaadka.

Sidoo kale waxaa macquul ah in koodhkaagu dhacay. Hadday saas tahay, waa inaad codsataa koodh cusub ood ka hesho maamulkaaga caafimaadka.
verification_code_alerts.network_connection_body: Waa inaad ku xirantaa WiFi si aad u gudbiso koodhka xaqiijinta.
verification_code_alerts.unknown_body: Cilad aan la filayn ayaa dhacday. Fadlan markale iskuday.
